com.revivedstandards.commands

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revivedstandards.commands.Command
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BulletCommand, MoveCommand, PauseCommand

    public abstract class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    This framework enables the user to define custom game actions encapsulated by Commands and bind arbitrary controls to them.
